<div class="container home">

  <div class="row">
    <section class="col-xs-12 text-xs-center presentation">
      <h1 class="text-xs-center">Euthymia</h1>
      <%= image_tag 'angel.svg', class: 'text-xs-center space', height: 250 %>
      <p class="text-xs-center lead text-muted space">Because knowing your emotions matters</p>
    </section>
  </div>

  <section class="description row">

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6  space-4x">
      <p class="text-justify">
        It's great to write about you, it increase your knowing about yourself. But sometimes even we don't know, because of the mix of feelings we get.
      </p>
      <p class="text-justify">
        Sometimes we just don't see where we are heading with our emotions.
      </p>
      <p class="space-2x text-xs-center">
        <%= image_tag 'unicorn.svg', height: 100 %>
      </p>
      <p class="lead space-2x text-xs-center text-orange">We are here to help you!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 get-started space-2x">
      <div class="text-xs-center">
        <h2 class="text-xs-center space-4x">Ready ?</h2>
        <p class="text-xs-center space"><%= image_tag 'cool.svg', height: 70 %></p>
        <%= link_to 'Get Started', new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn-lg btn-xs-block btn-orange btn-hg btn space' %>
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>

</div>
<!-- end container -->

<div class="container-fluid  features">

  <div class="row">

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4 space-2x text-xs-center">
      <%= image_tag 'features/pencil.svg', height: 70 %>
      <p class="text-xs-center space lead">
        Markdown
      </p>
      <p>
        With markdown syntax support you can write and format your entries as you go. Making easier to read back.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4 space-2x text-xs-center">
      <%= image_tag 'features/bookmark.svg', height: 70 %>
      <p class="lead space">
        Bookmark your entries
      </p>
      <p>
        Make easy to remember the great times and the important notes about you. At a click of distance.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4 space-2x text-xs-center">
      <%= image_tag 'features/key.svg', height: 70 %>
      <p class="lead space">Everything is private</p>
      <p>Your journals and entries are only private. No more messing with permissions or leting something out because you forgot to toggle something.</p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
      <hr>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row space-4x">

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 text-xs-center space-bottom-3x">
      <%= image_tag 'features/analysis.svg', height: 100 %>
      <h2 class="space">Natural language analysis</h2>
      <p class="lead">
        To help you indentifying you mixed emotions, we use the powerful
        <a href="https://indico.io" target="_blank">Indico</a>
        API to process the entries.
        <strong>But do not worry !</strong>
        no data is kept on their side It is used to identify the 4 more common emotions:
        <i>Joy</i>,
        <i>surprise</i>,
        <i>sadness</i>,
        <i>fear</i>
        and
        <i>anger</i>
        and the overall sentiment about the entry.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>

</div>
<!-- end container fluid -->
